import React from 'react'
import {
    CardContainer,
    Cardh1,
    CardItems,
    CardItem,
    CardImg,
    CardText,
    CardName,
    CardPrice,
    CardYear,
} from './style';

const ProductCard = (name, price) => {
    return (
        <CardContainer>
            <Cardh1>XMAS DEAL</Cardh1>
            <CardItems>
                <CardItem>
                    <CardImg href={src}></CardImg>
                    <CardText>
                        <CardName>{name}</CardName>
                        <CardPrice>{price}</CardPrice>  
                    </CardText>
                    <CardYear>2021</CardYear>
                </CardItem>
            </CardItems>
        </CardContainer>
    )
}

export default ProductCard
